locality: Kangding Xian: Between the cities of Luding and Kangding along the Dadu River.
On mountainside above Jegading (nonsacred); mixed coniferous forest.
South-facing slope on north wall of Adong River valley, below trail, before trail dips to cross river. Edge of scrub-oak transition; light grazing.
